<article id="post-768187" class="post-768187 digital-library type-digital-library status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry category-architecture-and-hardware category-artificial-intelligence-machine-learning category-computing-applications issue-july-2025 section-sustainability-and-computing">

			
<header class="article-header article-header--default">
	<div class="article-header__inner container">
		<div class="article-header__section"><a href="https://cacm.acm.org/section/sustainability-and-computing/">Sustainability and Computing</a></div>
		<div class="article-header__topic-and-issue-section">
			<span class="article-header__topic">
			<a href="https://cacm.acm.org/category/architecture-and-hardware/">Architecture and Hardware</a>			</span>
			<span class="article-header__issue-section">
							</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="article-header__title">Making AI Less &#8216;Thirsty&#8217;</h1>
					<div class="article-header__subtitle"><p>Uncovering and addressing the secret water footprint of AI models.</p>
</div>
		
		<div class="article-header__meta">
			<div class="article-header__byline">
				By <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/pengfei-li/" title="Posts by Pengfei Li" class="author url fn" rel="author">Pengfei Li</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/jianyi-yang/" title="Posts by Jianyi Yang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Jianyi Yang</a>, <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/mohammad-a-islam/" title="Posts by Mohammad A. Islam" class="author url fn" rel="author">Mohammad A. Islam</a>, and <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/shaolei-ren/" title="Posts by Shaolei Ren" class="author url fn" rel="author">Shaolei Ren</a>			</div>
			<div class="article-header__posted-on">
				<span class="posted-on">Posted <time datetime="2025-06-17T13:41:45-04:00">Jun 17 2025</time></span>			</div>
		</div>

			<figure class="article-header__figure">
			<div class="image-wrapper image-wrapper--widescreen"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.SSR_.Less-Thirsty-S.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="servers immersed in liquid" loading="eager" decoding="async" srcset="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.SSR_.Less-Thirsty-S.jpg 2400w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.SSR_.Less-Thirsty-S.jpg?resize=300,169 300w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.SSR_.Less-Thirsty-S.jpg?resize=768,432 768w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.SSR_.Less-Thirsty-S.jpg?resize=1024,576 1024w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.SSR_.Less-Thirsty-S.jpg?resize=1536,864 1536w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/061225.SSR_.Less-Thirsty-S.jpg?resize=2048,1152 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></div>		</figure>

